        <abstract> 
<p>Is much obliged for AG’s two memoirs ["Mémoire sur le reptile découvert par M. Frossard", <hi rend="italic">Nouv. Arch. Mus. Hist. Nat.</hi> 3 (1867): 21–40; <hi rend="italic">Bull. Soc. Géol. France</hi> 2d ser. 24 (1867): 397–400].</p> 
            <p>All "inosculating forms" are very interesting to CD.</p>
            <p>Agrees with AG on the importance of attempts to affiliate extinct and existing species.</p> 
<p>Will send French edition of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> when published.</p> 
        </abstract>
